commonMistakes.correction:
**Forgetting foreign key field**:
   ```prisma
   // WRONG! Missing authorId
   model Post {
     id     Int  @id
     author User @relation(fields: [authorId], references: [id])
   }

   // CORRECT!
   model Post {
     id       Int  @id
     authorId Int  // Foreign key field
     author   User @relation(fields: [authorId], references: [id])
   }
   ```

**Wrong array syntax**:
   ```prisma
   // WRONG!
   model User {
     posts Post  // Missing brackets!
   }

   // CORRECT!
   model User {
     posts Post[]  // Array of posts
   }
   ```
